(549, 1, '2012-02-29 20:39:49', '2012-02-29 20:39:49', '<p><strong><a class="contentlink" href="mailto:rpaulino@sdlyons.com" id="RobertPaulino" name="RobertPaulino">Robert J. Paulino</a></strong> is a Certified Forensic Locksmith and an ASE-Certified Automotive Technician with a unique combination of an extensive locksmithing background and a strong hands-on automotive background. Mr. Paulino has over 20 years&rsquo; experience in automotive and residential locksmithing and has over 25 years&rsquo; experience in automotive repair. He has extensive training in vehicle locking systems, electronic vehicle security systems, and vehicle fire origin and cause. Mr. Paulino is a court qualified expert in the field of automotive forensic analysis. He is widely respected for his expertise in forensic automotive locksmithing, vehicle collision repair evaluation, vehicle fire origin and cause, and mechanical systems analysis.</p>', 'Robert J. Paulino', 'Certified Forensic Locksmith', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'robert-j-paulino', '', '', '2012-03-01 18:45:55', '2012-03-01 18:45:55', '', 0, '/?post_type=technician-bio&#038;p=549', 0, 'technician-bio', '', 0),
