(555, 1, '2012-02-29 20:08:43', '2012-02-29 20:08:43', '<p><strong><a class="contentlink" href="mailto:cborelli@sdlyons.com" id="ChristopherBorelli" name="ChristopherBorelli">Christopher Borelli</a></strong> is a Mechanical Engineer (B.S.M.E.) and an ACTAR-accredited Accident Reconstructionist, and is the managing director of the Accident Reconstruction division of S. D. Lyons, Inc. Mr. Borelli received his primary education in accident reconstruction from the Northwestern University in Chicago, Illinois, and receives continuing education at various universities and related associations around the country. He has provided expert testimony for trials and arbitrations in Massachusetts, Rhode Island, and Connecticut. Mr. Borelli has over 14 years of experience reconstructing motor vehicle accidents.</p>\r\n', 'Christopher Borelli', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '541-revision-2', '', '', '2012-02-29 20:08:43', '2012-02-29 20:08:43', '', 541, '/2012/02/541-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
