(1021, 3, '2013-04-16 20:51:28', '2013-04-16 20:51:28', '<h3>Fast, accurate assessments from industry experts at a fraction of the cost.</h3>\r\n<p>S. D. Lyons serves New England and eastern New York, delivering expert automotive forensic analysis and expert court testimony in several specialty areas, including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Vehicle Accident Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Mechanical/Electrical Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Vehicle Theft Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Vehicle Fire Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Physical Damage Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Report Review Claims</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our qualified experts perform not only comprehensive vehicle examinations, but also exhaustive research, incident scene inspections, and review of background information to ensure a thorough and impartial analysis. Our support staff provides our Engineers and Technicians with the resources and data they require, while offering prompt response to technical and other inquiries posed by our clients. With the capability for paperless invoicing and reporting, we&rsquo;ll deliver your results in the timeliest manner possible. Additionally, S. D. Lyons can provide, at no charge, seminars pertaining to any of our specialty areas.</p>\r\n', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'services', '', '', '2013-04-16 21:59:36', '2013-04-16 21:59:36', '', 1015, 'http://www.accidentreview.com/?page_id=1021', 0, 'page', '', 0),
