(1025, 3, '2013-04-16 20:52:46', '2013-04-16 20:52:46', '<h3>Seamless, sophisticated solutions for today&#39;s automotive insurance industry.</h3>\r\n<h4>Safe, secure, and speedy claim reviews.</h4>\r\n<p>With AccidentReview.com&#39;s safe and secure online portal, insurance claim agents can obtain accurate, expert opinions within 24 hours &hellip; all at a low flat rate of $200.</p>\r\n<p>Available only to insurance companies, AccidentReview.com&#39;s exclusive online system provides the perfect solution for claims agents that need a fast yet accurate forensic assessment.</p>\r\n<p>Registered users will have access to a host of online claims management features, including claims tracking, access to your assigned claim representative, and more. Once your case is submitted, our automotive forensic experts will examine the data, documents, photographs, and any other pertinent information provided, and render an opinion within one business day.</p>\r\n<h4>Prompt and professional customer support.</h4>\r\n<p>Every single member of AccidentReview.com&#39;s staff is fully committed to providing our clients with the prompt and professional customer support they need to arrive at an accurate, cost-effective claim decision.</p>\r\n<p>Our highly-qualified experts perform comprehensive vehicle examinations, exhaustive research, incident scene inspections, and review of background information to ensure a thorough and impartial analysis on each claim review.</p>\r\n<p>Supporting our accredited Accident Reconstructionists and Automotive Forensic Technicians is our highly-trained office staff. They provide the research, analysis, and technical expertise that enables our Technicians and Engineers to expediently conduct their analyses and ensure the most accurate reports are delivered in a timely fashion.</p>\r\n', 'Customer Support', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'customer-support', '', '', '2013-04-16 22:06:28', '2013-04-16 22:06:28', '', 1015, 'http://www.accidentreview.com/?page_id=1025', 0, 'page', '', 0),
